---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="GentleDo — Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for the GentleDo app."
  path="/en/privacy/gentledo"
>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-2">GentleDo Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-deep-ocean/40 dark:text-driftwood/40 mb-10">Last updated: March 29, 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-deep-ocean/80 dark:text-driftwood/80">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">1. Overview</h2>
        <p>GentleDo ("the App") is a productivity app developed by babipa. This Privacy Policy explains how your information is handled when you use the App.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">GentleDo does not collect any personal information.</p>
        <p class="mb-3">All data created within the App (tasks, daily logs, settings, etc.) is stored exclusively on your device and is never transmitted to external servers.</p>
        <p class="font-medium text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood text-sm mb-2">Data stored locally on your device:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm pl-2">
          <li>Task lists and related information (title, memo, priority, category, estimated time, etc.)</li>
          <li>Daily energy check-in records</li>
          <li>Momentum scores</li>
          <li>Defer history</li>
          <li>App settings (language, theme, notification preferences, etc.)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">3. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>All data is stored locally on your device using a SQLite database. No data is transmitted to cloud servers, external databases, or third-party services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">4. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
        <p>GentleDo does not share any data with third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">5. Notifications</h2>
        <p>The App uses local notifications. Notifications are processed entirely on your device and do not use push notification servers. Notification permissions can be changed at any time in your device settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">6. Analytics and Tracking</h2>
        <p>GentleDo does not include any user analytics, tracking, or advertising.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>GentleDo does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">8. Data Deletion</h2>
        <p>Uninstalling the App will delete all data stored on your device. You can back up your data using the export feature in the App's settings before uninstalling.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">9. Changes</h2>
        <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated. Changes will be communicated through App updates.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood mb-2">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-deep-ocean dark:text-driftwood">babipanote@gmail.com</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
